> Single source of truth. Paste this at the start of every vibe coding session.

---

## What we are building

A college-only clothes platform for CIT Chennai students with 3 modules:
1. **Borrow & Lend** вЂ” post clothes to lend, request a borrow, approve/reject/return
2. **Item Request Board** вЂ” post "I need X", others respond, requester marks fulfilled
3. **Lost & Found** вЂ” post lost or found clothes with a photo, browse and claim

---

## Rules

- CIT Chennai students only вЂ” @citchennai.net Google accounts
- No anonymous posting вЂ” every user is identified
- No payments вЂ” platform is free to use
- No Docker
- Free tier only

