## API contract

Base URL: `/api/v1`

### Standard error shape
```json
{ "error": "CODE", "message": "Human readable" }
```

### Standard pagination shape
```json
{ "items": [], "total": 0, "page": 1, "page_size": 20, "total_pages": 1 }
```

### Error codes
```
UNAUTHORIZED         вЂ” missing or invalid JWT
FORBIDDEN            вЂ” insufficient role
INCOMPLETE_PROFILE   вЂ” must complete profile first
NOT_FOUND            вЂ” resource does not exist
BORROW_CONFLICT      вЂ” dates overlap with existing approved request
ALREADY_RESPONDED    вЂ” user already responded to this request
UPLOAD_FAILED        вЂ” storage upload error
```

