### Borrow & Lend

```
GET    /borrow/listings              вЂ” no auth, paginated, ?type=&size=&page=
POST   /borrow/listings              вЂ” JWT, multipart (image optional)
DELETE /borrow/listings/{id}         вЂ” JWT, owner only, cannot delete if borrowed
GET    /borrow/listings/{id}         вЂ” no auth
POST   /borrow/listings/{id}/request вЂ” JWT, not owner, body: {reason,borrow_from,borrow_until}
                                       check: borrow_until - borrow_from <= max_borrow_days
                                       check: no overlapping approved request в†’ BORROW_CONFLICT
GET    /borrow/my-requests           вЂ” JWT, paginated
GET    /borrow/my-listings-requests  вЂ” JWT, paginated (incoming requests on my listings)
PATCH  /borrow/requests/{id}/approve вЂ” JWT, listing owner only
                                       в†’ listing status = borrowed
PATCH  /borrow/requests/{id}/reject  вЂ” JWT, listing owner only
PATCH  /borrow/requests/{id}/return  вЂ” JWT, listing owner only
                                       в†’ listing status = available
                                       в†’ request status = returned
```

